OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780575067
OL,3,CMan convicted of murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cpartner to death in fit of rage
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of the
OL,7,Fmurder of his partner, Annabel Rook,
OL,8,F46, after stabbing her to death in a
OL,9,Ffit of rage.
OL,11,FClifton George was also convicted of
OL,12,Farson with intent to endanger life,
OL,13,Fafter attempting to set the couple's
OL,14,Fhouse in Stoke Newington alight
OL,15,Fthrough a gas explosion.
OL,17,FAt 04:57am last year, police, the
OL,18,FLondon Fire Brigade and the London
OL,19,FAmbulance Service all attended reports
OL,20,Fof a gas explosion at their house.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780575067
OL,3,CMan convicted of murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cpartner to death in fit of rage
OL,6,FThere, they found George bleeding
OL,7,Fheavily from his neck and arms while
OL,8,Fattempting to stab himself, who told
OL,9,Fofficers at the scene that Rook had
OL,10,Fdied "because I killed her."
OL,12,FAn earlier argument between the pair
OL,13,Fhad escalated into a brutal attak,
OL,14,Fwhere George had repeatedly punched
OL,15,FAnnabel and attempted to strangle her.
OL,17,FShe was subsequently stabbed 22 times.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780575067
OL,3,CMan convicted of murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cpartner to death in fit of rage
OL,6,FIn the frenzied aftermath, he started
OL,7,Fa fire and set off a gas cannister,
OL,8,Ftriggering an explosion that ripped
OL,9,Fthrough their home and woke up
OL,10,Fneighbours along the street.
OL,12,FGeorge was convicted at Snaresbrook
OL,13,FCrown Court, and will be sentenced
OL,14,Fthere on 9 June.
OL,16,FRook was a charity worker, who had
OL,17,Fspelled out in a heartbreaking letter
OL,18,Fhow she lived in fear of her abusive
OL,19,Fpartner's temper and wanted to end
OL,20,Ftheir 10-year relationship.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780575067
OL,3,CMan convicted of murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cpartner to death in fit of rage
OL,6,FShe wrote to partner Clifton George,
OL,7,Fsaying they did not make each other
OL,8,Fhappy any more and telling him:
OL,9,F"However hard I tried, I seemed to
OL,10,Fmake you angry."
OL,12,FBut Ms Rook's letter was never sent,
OL,13,Fand was only discovered by police on
OL,14,Fher laptop after she had been beaten,
OL,15,Fthrottled, and stabbed to death by
OL,16,FGeorge in the living room of their
OL,17,FStoke Newington home.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@PO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780575067
OL,3,CMan convicted of murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cpartner to death in fit of rage
OL,6,FDamning evidence was aired during the
OL,7,Ffour-week trial detailing George's
OL,8,Fshort temper, his tendency to get
OL,9,Fangry at trivial things, and incidents
OL,10,Fwhen he had verbally and physically
OL,11,Fattacked Ms Rook.
OL,13,FProsecutor William Emlyn Jones KC said
OL,14,Fthe unsent letter was "a heartbreaking
OL,15,Fdescription of a woman reluctantly
OL,16,Fletting go of her dream of a happy
OL,17,Flife with her partner.
OL,26,@vD@WOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1780575067
OL,3,CMan convicted of murder after stabbing
OL,4,Cpartner to death in fit of rage
OL,6,F"It is not angry, or hurtful ` it is
OL,7,Fexpressed as an attempt to be
OL,8,Freasonable and accepting that the
OL,9,Frelationship just isn't going to work."
OL,11,FIn the letter, she suggested a
OL,12,Fseparation and wrote: "A year ago we
OL,13,Fcame to the decision we weren't making
OL,14,Feach other happy.
OL,16,F"Somehow love wasn't enough. We
OL,17,Fcouldn't reach each other."
OL,19,FShe added: "My heart is broken."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@gO]tD@WOUxD@AOUyD@[O]{D@LOU{D@
OL,26,A`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/15
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
